<!--프랑스_코뮌_정보-->
{{TemplateMapping
| mapToClass = Settlement
| mappings =
	{{ConstantMapping | ontologyProperty = country | value = France }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 이름 | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 레지옹 | ontologyProperty = region }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 데파르트망 | ontologyProperty = department }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 아롱디스망 | ontologyProperty = arrondissement }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 칸톤 | ontologyProperty = canton }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 우편번호 | ontologyProperty = postalCode }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 시장 | ontologyProperty = mayor }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 홈페이지 | ontologyProperty = foaf:homepage }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 인구 | ontologyProperty = populationTotal }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 면적 | ontologyProperty = area | unit = squareKilometre  }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 평균고도 | ontologyProperty = elevation | unit = metre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 최소고도 | ontologyProperty = minimumElevation | unit = metre }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = elevation_max_m | ontologyProperty = maximumElevation | unit = metre }}
end}}
